title: KAQTU Design
description:
Your platform for stylish interiors. Discover unique design ideas powered by AI, real-time personalized room planning, and a curated selection of furniture and home accessories. With advanced AI tools, KAQTU makes it easy to find designs, layouts, and products tailored to your taste and needs.

Focusing on sustainability and quality, KAQTU offers everything you need to transform your living space into a stylish sanctuary.
